e(route_points)\n  \n# Calculate the total difference\nvdist <- nodeDiff(alt)\nsum(vdist)\n\n\n\n\n\n### Section 4: Output -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n# Calculate the toughness\ntough <- toughness(vdist, route_details$dist)\ntough\n\nplot(ahn)\nplot(route_points, add=T)\n\n",
